          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14713367/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14713367/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/50614031/" class=" " title="倦炉">倦炉</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="14713367">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">买这本书为的就是求个简单通俗，对于那些动辄就引经据典的著作还是望而生畏的。通俗，明白，客观这就是书的特点，也是买书时候看重的。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-10-01 11:59</span>
                  
                </p>
